<div class="av" style="color:var(--cy);">U</div>
<div><div class="chat-b">Yes, generate a dashboard with layout, data display, and action components.</div><div class="chat-t">10:25 AM</div></div>
</div>
<div class="ag-act" style="margin-left:48px;margin-bottom:12px;">
<span class="ag-act-i">⟳</span>
<span>Composing dashboard layout...</span>
</div>
<div class="chat-m" style="margin-bottom:12px;margin-left:48px;">
