<div class="mx-msg">
<div class="mx-msg-h"><span class="mx-msg-n" style="color:var(--yl);">Carol</span><span class="mx-msg-t">10:25 AM</span></div>
<div class="mx-msg-b">Can we add a Timeline component to the registry? I need it for the admin dashboard.</div>
</div>
<div class="mx-msg">
<div class="mx-msg-h"><span class="mx-msg-n">Alice</span><span class="mx-msg-t">10:26 AM</span><span class="mx-msg-r">Mod</span></div>
<div class="mx-msg-b">Sure! I'll add it to the backlog. The Timeline is already in the base primitives, just needs to be registered.</div>
</div>
<div class="mx-msg" style="background:rgba(52,207,230,0.05);border-color:var(--cy);">
<div class="mx-msg-h"><span class="mx-msg-n" style="color:var(--em);">🤖 Bot</span><span class="mx-msg-t">10:26 AM</span><span class="mx-msg-r" style="background:rgba(255,106,61,0.15);color:var(--em);">Bot</span></div>
<div class="mx-msg-b">📎 <strong>Component Request Logged</strong><br>Request: Timeline component registration<br>Status: Added to backlog<br>Priority: Medium</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="cht-f">
<div class="cht-fi"><input type="text" placeholder="Message #general..." hx-post="/matrix/send" hx-trigger="keydown[key=='Enter']" hx-vals='{"room":"#general:flint.dev"}'></div>
<button class="btn btn-p">Send</button>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="demo-code">{"type":"matrix_chat","room":"#general:flint.dev","members":24,"online":12,"hx_post":"/matrix/send","hx_vals":{"room":"#general:flint.dev"}}</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>

<!-- Video Section -->
<section id="video" class="sec">
<div class="sec-h"><div class="icon">🎬</div><h3>Video Streaming</h3><span class="tag">Media</span></div>

<div class="comp-grid">
<div class="comp-item" style="grid-column:1/-1;">
<h4>🎬 Video Player</h4>
<div class="demo">
<div class="demo-label">Streaming Interface</div>
<div class="vp">
<div style="font-size:48px;opacity:0.3;">▶</div>
<div class="vp-b">
<button class="vp-btn">▶</button>
<button class="vp-btn">⏸</button>
<div class="vp-bar"><div class="vp-bar-f" style="width:35%"></div></div>
<div class="vp-ct">04:23 / 12:45</div>
<button class="vp-btn">⚙</button>
<button class="vp-btn">⛶</button>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="demo-code">{"type":"video_player","src":"/stream/video.mp4","controls":true,"progress":35,"hx_get":"/api/video/progress"}</div>
</div>

<div class="comp-item">
<h4>🎬 Video Editor Timeline</h4>
<div class="demo">
<div class="demo-label">Timeline Interface</div>
<div class="ie-t">
<button class="ie-t-b on">Select</button><button class="ie-t-b">Split</button><button class="ie-t-b">Delete</button>
<button class="ie-t-b">Undo</button><button class="ie-t-b">Redo</button>
<div style="width:1px;background:var(--s4);margin:0 4px;"></div>
<button class="ie-t-b">🎵</button><button class="ie-t-b">🎬</button><button class="ie-t-b">🎨</button>
</div>
<div class="ie-c" style="aspect-ratio:16/9;background:var(--s3);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;position:relative;overflow:hidden;border-radius:8px;">
<div style="font-size:48px;opacity:0.3;">🎬</div>
</div>
<div class="ve-tl">
<div class="ve-tl-w" style="position:relative;flex:1;">
<div class="ve-tl-t">
<div class="ve-tl-s" style="height:60%"></div><div class="ve-tl-s" style="height:80%"></div><div class="ve-tl-s" style="height:40%"></div>
<div class="ve-tl-s" style="height:90%"></div><div class="ve-tl-s" style="height:55%"></div><div class="ve-tl-s" style="height:70%"></div>
<div class="ve-tl-s" style="height:45%"></div><div class="ve-tl-s" style="height:85%"></div><div class="ve-tl-s" style="height:60%"></div>
<div class="ve-tl-s" style="height:75%"></div><div class="ve-tl-s" style="height:50%"></div><div class="ve-tl-s" style="height:80%"></div>
<div class="ve-tl-s" style="height:65%"></div><div class="ve-tl-s" style="height:90%"></div><div class="ve-tl-s" style="height:55%"></div>
<div class="ve-tl-s" style="height:70%"></div><div class="ve-tl-s" style="height:45%"></div><div class="ve-tl-s" style="height:85%"></div>
<div class="ve-tl-s" style="height:60%"></div><div class="ve-tl-s" style="height:75%"></div>
</div>
<div class="ve-tl-c" style="left:35%"></div>
</div>
<div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--txtd);font-family:var(--fm);min-width:60px;text-align:right;">04:23</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="demo-code">{"type":"video_editor","tracks":["Video","Audio"],"duration":"12:45","playhead":"04:23","hx_post":"/api/video/edit"}</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>

<!-- Image Section -->
<section id="image" class="sec">
<div class="sec-h"><div class="icon">🖼️</div><h3>Image Display & Editing</h3><span class="tag">Media</span></div>

<div class="comp-grid">
<div class="comp-item" style="grid-column:1/-1;">
<h4>🖼️ Image Gallery</h4>
<div class="demo">
<div class="demo-label">Grid Gallery</div>
<div class="ig">
<div class="ig-i"><div style="width:100%;height:100%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:24px;background:var(--s3);">🖼️</div><div class="ig-i-o"><div class="ig-i-b"><button>🔍</button><button>✏️</button><button>🗑️</button></div></div></div>
<div class="ig-i"><div style="width:100%;height:100%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:24px;background:var(--s3);">📊</div><div class="ig-i-o"><div class="ig-i-b"><button>🔍</button><button>✏️</button><button>🗑️</button></div></div></div>
<div class="ig-i"><div style="width:100%;height:100%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:24px;background:var(--s3);">🎨</div><div class="ig-i-o"><div class="ig-i-b"><button>🔍</button><button>✏️</button><button>🗑️</button></div></div></div>
<div class="ig-i"><div style="width:100%;height:100%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:24px;background:var(--s3);">📄</div><div class="ig-i-o"><div class="ig-i-b"><button>🔍</button><button>✏️</button><button>🗑️</button></div></div></div>
<div class="ig-i"><div style="width:100%;height:100%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:24px;background:var(--s3);">🗺️</div><div class="ig-i-o"><div class="ig-i-b"><button>🔍</button><button>✏️</button><button>🗑️</button></div></div></div>
<div class="ig-i" style="border-style:dashed;border-color:var(--txtd);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;cursor:pointer;"><div style="text-align:center;"><div style="font-size:24px;margin-bottom:4px;">+</div><div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--txtd);">Upload</div></div></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="demo-code">{"type":"image_gallery","images":[...],"actions":["view","edit","delete"],"hx_post":"/api/gallery/upload"}</div>
</div>

<div class="comp-item">
<h4>🖼️ Image Editor</h4>
<div class="demo">
<div class="demo-label">Editing Interface</div>
<div class="ie-t">
<button class="ie-t-b on">Crop</button><button class="ie-t-b">Rotate</button><button class="ie-t-b">Resize</button>
<div style="width:1px;background:var(--s4);margin:0 4px;"></div>
<button class="ie-t-b">Brightness</button><button class="ie-t-b">Contrast</button><button class="ie-t-b">Saturation</button>
<div style="width:1px;background:var(--s4);margin:0 4px;"></div>
<button class="ie-t-b">🎨 Filters</button>
</div>
<div class="ie-c" style="aspect-ratio:4/3;">
<div style="font-size:48px;opacity:0.3;">🖼️</div>
<div style="position:absolute;bottom:12px;left:12px;right:12px;display:flex;gap:8px;">
<div class="fg" style="flex:1;margin:0;"><label class="lbl" style="font-size:10px;">Brightness</label><input type="range" class="rng" min="0" max="200" value="100"></div>
<div class="fg" style="flex:1;margin:0;"><label class="lbl" style="font-size:10px;">Contrast</label><input type="range" class="rng" min="0" max="200" value="100"></div>
</div>
</div>
<div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;margin-top:12px;">
<button class="btn btn-ghost btn-sm">Reset</button>
<div style="display:flex;gap:8px;">
<button class="btn btn-s btn-sm">Download</button>
<button class="btn btn-p btn-sm">Save</button>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="demo-code">{"type":"image_editor","tools":["crop","rotate","brightness","contrast"],"hx_post":"/api/image/edit"}</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>

</div></main></div>
</body></html>
